字符函数.Section-特殊符号分割截取:
### Section-特殊符号分割截取

```cpp
String Section(String str, String split, Integer start, Integer end = -1, Integer flags = 0)
```

**说明：**

> 返回字符串包含从位置开始到位置结束的字段

**参数：**

| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明  |
| ------ | ---- | ---- |
| <div style="width:50pt">str</div>    | String  | 原字符串 |
| split  | String  | 分割符 |
| start  | Integer | 开始位置 |
| end    | Integer | 结束位置，默认-1表示到字符串结尾 |
| flags  | Integer | <a href="/helper?product_id=999&search=字符串分割选项&type=search" target=_blank>字符串分割选项</a>，如：Enum_SectionDefault、Enum_SectionSkipEmpty、Enum_SectionIncludeLeadingSep、Enum_SectionIncludeTrailingSep、Enum_SectionCaseInsensitiveSeps。 |

**返回值：**

| 类型 | 说明 |
| ---- | ---- |
| String | 字符串包含从位置开始到位置结束的字段 |

**示例：**

```cpp
Events
    OnReady()
    {
        String baseStr = " ~!@#$%^&*()_+`1234567890-=qwertyuiop{}|[]\\ ASDFGHJKL:\";'zxcvbnm<>?,./~！@#￥%&*（）——+·-={}|【】、：“；‘《》？，。/ QWERTYUIOP ";
        String secStr = Section(baseStr, "/", 0, -1, Enum_SectionDefault);
        Print("Section,size:" + Text(Len(secStr)) + ",secStr:" + secStr);
        secStr = Section(baseStr, "/", 0, 0, Enum_SectionDefault);
        Print("Section,size:" + Text(Len(secStr)) + ",secStr:" + secStr);
        secStr = Section(baseStr, "/", 0, 1, Enum_SectionDefault);
        Print("Section,size:" + Text(Len(secStr)) + ",secStr:" + secStr);
        secStr = Section(baseStr, "/", 0, 2, Enum_SectionDefault);
        Print("Section,size:" + Text(Len(secStr)) + ",secStr:" + secStr);
        secStr = Section(baseStr, "/", 1, 1, Enum_SectionDefault);
        Print("Section,size:" + Text(Len(secStr)) + ",secStr:" + secStr);
        secStr = Section(baseStr, "/", 1, 2, Enum_SectionDefault);
        Print("Section,size:" + Text(Len(secStr)) + ",secStr:" + secStr);
        secStr = Section(baseStr, "/", 2, 2, Enum_SectionDefault);
        Print("Section,size:" + Text(Len(secStr)) + ",secStr:" + secStr);

        secStr = Section(baseStr, "/", 1, 1, Enum_SectionDefault);
        Print("Section,size:" + Text(Len(secStr)) + ",secStr:" + secStr);
        secStr = Section(baseStr, "/", 1, 1, Enum_SectionIncludeLeadingSep);
        Print("Section,size:" + Text(Len(secStr)) + ",secStr:" + secStr);
        secStr = Section(baseStr, "/", 1, 1, Enum_SectionIncludeTrailingSep);
        Print("Section,size:" + Text(Len(secStr)) + ",secStr:" + secStr);
        secStr = Section(baseStr, "/", 1, 1, BitOr(Enum_SectionIncludeLeadingSep, Enum_SectionIncludeTrailingSep));
        Print("Section,size:" + Text(Len(secStr)) + ",secStr:" + secStr);

        secStr = Section(baseStr, "Q", 1, 1, Enum_SectionDefault);
        Print("Section,size:" + Text(Len(secStr)) + ",secStr:" + secStr);
        secStr = Section(baseStr, "Q", 1, 1, Enum_SectionCaseInsensitiveSeps);
        Print("Section,size:" + Text(Len(secStr)) + ",secStr:" + secStr);
    } 
```

