Map映射表.MapLowerBound-映射表第一个大于或等于key的元素的索引获取:
### MapLowerBound-映射表第一个大于或等于key的元素的索引获取

```cpp
Integer MapLowerBound(MapRef mapValue, Integer key)
Integer MapLowerBound(MapRef mapValue, String key)
```

**说明：**

> 获取映射表中第一个大于或等于key的元素的索引。

**参数：**

| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明 |
| ------ | ---- | ---- |
| mapValue | MapRef | 映射表 |
| key      | Integer、String | 键值 |

**返回值：**

| 类型 | 说明 |
| ---- | ---- |
| Integer | 第一个大于或等于Key的元素的索引，获取失败返回无效值 |

**示例：**

```cpp
Events
    OnInit()
    {
        Map<Integer, String> mapValues;
        mapValues[0] = "a";
        mapValues[2] = "b";
        mapValues[4] = "c";
        mapValues[8] = "d";
        String val;
        //获取映射表中第一个大于或等于key的元素的索引
        Integer pos = MapLowerBound(mapValues, 9);
        Print("MapLowerBound,pos:" + Text(pos));
        Bool ret = GetMapValue(mapValues, pos, val);
        Print("GetMapValue:" + IIFString(ret, "True", "False") + "," + val);
        pos = MapLowerBound(mapValues, -1);
        Print("MapLowerBound,pos:" + Text(pos));
        ret = GetMapValue(mapValues, pos, val);
        Print("GetMapValue:" + IIFString(ret, "True", "False") + "," + val);
        pos = MapLowerBound(mapValues, 0);
        Print("MapLowerBound,pos:" + Text(pos));
        ret = GetMapValue(mapValues, pos, val);
        Print("GetMapValue:" + IIFString(ret, "True", "False") + "," + val);
        pos = MapLowerBound(mapValues, 1);
        Print("MapLowerBound,pos:" + Text(pos));
        ret = GetMapValue(mapValues, pos, val);
        Print("GetMapValue:" + IIFString(ret, "True", "False") + "," + val);
        pos = MapLowerBound(mapValues, 8);
        Print("MapLowerBound,pos:" + Text(pos));
        ret = GetMapValue(mapValues, pos, val);
        Print("GetMapValue:" + IIFString(ret, "True", "False") + "," + val);
    }
```

**输出：**

> MapLowerBound,pos:N/A<br>
> GetMapValue:False,<br>
> MapLowerBound,pos:0<br>
> GetMapValue:True,a<br>
> MapLowerBound,pos:0<br>
> GetMapValue:True,a<br>
> MapLowerBound,pos:1<br>
> GetMapValue:True,b<br>
> MapLowerBound,pos:3<br>
> GetMapValue:True,d

